- [ ] Visual identity is consistent across all touchpoints
- [ ] Brand voice is authoritative, stoic, and masculine
- [ ] Messaging clearly communicates value proposition
- [ ] Color palette is properly applied and accessible
- [ ] Typography hierarchy is consistent and readable
- [ ] Logo usage follows established guidelines
- [ ] Content reflects brand personality and values
- [ ] Marketing materials maintain professional standards
- [ ] Brand guidelines are documented and accessible
